  <h3>Extraordinary Liver Support Backed By Research</h3>
  <p>
    Supplying the liver with targeted vitamins, minerals, and plant compounds — with specific foods, teas, and powerful antioxidants (as found in fruits like wolfberries) — has been shown in scientific studies to provide liver-protective effects<sup>1-3</sup>, improve antioxidant status<sup>4,5</sup>, and reduce oxidative stress<sup>6-9</sup>. We recommend focusing on adding wolfberry to the diet if at all possible.
  </p>
